---
// Gift registry — with icons
---

<section id="regalos" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Regalos</h2>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#c0c0c0]/60"></span>
      <span class="text-[#c0c0c0] text-sm">✧</span>
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#c0c0c0]/60"></span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[#0a2540]/50 italic text-sm mb-10">
      Tu presencia es lo más importante. Pero si deseas tener un detalle con Jimena:
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
      <a
        href="https://www.amazon.com.mx/registries/gl/guest-view/2EOL1O5GFUK6E"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="glass-card p-6 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform block"
      >
        <svg class="w-7 h-7 mx-auto mb-3 text-[#0a2540]/30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-7" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2 7h20v5H2z" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 22V7" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7c-1.5-2-4-3.5-4-3.5S9.5 2 12 2s5 1.5 5 1.5S14 5 12 7z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-xs font-[Montserrat] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[#0a2540]/40 mb-2">Amazon</p>
        <p class="text-[#0a2540] text-sm">Ver lista →</p>
      </a>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7 mx-auto mb-3 text-[#0a2540]/30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="14" rx="2" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2 6l10 7 10-7" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-xs font-[Montserrat] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[#0a2540]/40 mb-2">En el evento</p>
        <p class="text-[#0a2540] text-sm">Lluvia de sobres</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
